Note Application

Software Prequisites:
 - Java 21 (Oracle openJDK 21)
 - gradle 8 & above
 - docker 
 - psql client


Set up project:
Step 1: clone the repository
Step 2: go to database folder in the project & run `docker -t build migration:v2 .`
Step 3: In the root project, run docker compose up
Step 4: build the project, ./gradlew build
Step 5: run the project ./gradlew bootRun
Step 6: use postman to call the api's
